

Installing couchdb

Ubuntu

$ sudo apt-get install couchdb

Supposing you have couchdb installed and running. This concerns only installing virtualenv for couchapp.

Make sure python virtual env is installed (sudo apt-get install python-virtualenv)


$ mkdir venv

$ virtualenv venv --distribute

$ source ./venv/bin/activate

(venv)$ pip install couchapp 


That's all.
